    title: "Diagnostic Techniques",
    level: 4,
    durationMinutes: 30,
    summary: "Use OBD-II scanners, live data, and systematic fault-finding to diagnose engine management faults. Understand fault codes, freeze frame data, and the six-step diagnostic process.",
