        visualCue: "Imagine a close-up of vernier caliper scales: the main scale reads 23 mm at the vernier zero. The 7th vernier line (0.14 mm) aligns exactly with a main scale line. Total reading: 23.14 mm. A digital caliper beside it displays 23.14 on an LCD screen."
