        visualCue: "Imagine a plate edge being prepared: left shows the raw plate with mill scale and rust. Centre shows a worker grinding the face clean. Right shows the bevelled edge with a 60° included angle, 2 mm root gap, and 1 mm root face marked with dimension lines."
