        visualCue: "Visualise four identical T-joint configurations each oriented differently: flat (joint horizontal, welding downward), horizontal (joint vertical, welding sideways), vertical (joint horizontal, welding upward), and overhead (joint horizontal, welding upward from below). Torch angle and direction arrows on each."
